# AI agent guardrails — kept locally so Claude Code reads them on every
# session, but not published. CLAUDE.md is the team's candid "how to
# work in this repo" memo (release pitfalls we've hit, tooling rules
# we've broken N times, CF Worker routing internals); it's not the
# contributor guide. A public-facing CONTRIBUTING.md, when needed,
# should be authored separately.
